      "content": "Review this Python code for:\n\n1. **Type Hints**:\n   - All function signatures typed\n   - Return types specified\n   - Optional[] for nullable values\n\n2. **Async/Await Usage** (if applicable):\n   - No blocking calls (time.sleep, requests.get, etc.)\n   - All async calls properly awaited\n   - Proper use of asyncio primitives\n\n3. **Error Handling**:\n   - Specific exceptions caught\n   - No bare except clauses\n   - Errors logged appropriately\n\n4. **PEP 8 Compliance**:\n   - Line length < 88 characters\n   - Proper naming conventions\n   - Consistent formatting\n\nProvide specific feedback with examples of improvements.",
      "target": "claude",
